libs.content: find_program(bison_executable bison doc "path to the bison executable")

find_library(openssl_library
                 names ssl_pic ssl ssleay32 ssleay32md
                 hints ${openssl_root_dir}/lib)

find_library(crypto_library
                 names crypto_pic crypto libeay32
                 hints ${openssl_root_dir}/lib)

find_library(resolv_library
                 names resolv
                 no_cmake_path
                 no_cmake_environment_path
                 hints ${with_glibc_path}/lib)
find_program(cat_executable cat doc "path to the executable")
